          "type": "verse",
          "sid": "MAT 2:22"
        },
        "But when Joseph heard that Archelaus had succeeded his father Herod as king of Judea, he was afraid to go there. He was given more instructions in a dream, so he went to the province of Galilee ",
        {
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "23",
          "type": "verse",
          "sid": "MAT 2:23"
        },
        {
