              "content": [
                "2.23: "
              ],
              "type": "char"
            },
            {
              "marker": "xt",
              "content": [
                "Mt 1.22; 4.13; Mk 1.9; Lk 1.26; 2.39; Jn 1.45; 1.46; 18.5."
              ],
              "type": "char"
            }
          ],
          "caller": "-"
        },
        "and made his home in a town named Nazareth. And so what the prophets had said came true: “He will be called a Nazarene.”"
      ]
